<p>Hi {{name}},</p>
<p>We received a request to reset your password. Click the button below to
  choose a new password. This link expires in
  {{expiresIn}}.</p>
<p><a
    href="{{resetLink}}"
    style="display:inline-block;padding:10px 20px;background:#007bff;color:#fff;text-decoration:none;border-radius:4px;"
  >Reset Password</a></p>
<p>If you did not request a password reset, simply ignore this email.</p>
<p>Thanks,<br />TiffinCRM Team</p>